&lt;p&gt;Given,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At the time of sunrise, Diksha and Arpita are sitting in a park with their backs facing each other. If the shadow of Diksha falls to the right of Arpita.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/01/F2_%20Rishabh_05-01-21_Savita_D57.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 358px; width: 450px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here we see Arpita is facing &lt;strong&gt;South&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hence, the correct answer is South.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the given information;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F6_Savita_Engineering_29-6-22_D15.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 329px; width: 418px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, in East Direction 37 + 22&amp;nbsp; = 59.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;He is 59 far from the starting point.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;East, 59 m&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to given conditions,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mousumi is facing east. She turns 135&amp;deg;&amp;nbsp;in clockwise direction. Further she turns another 225&amp;deg;&amp;nbsp;in anticlockwise direction.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/20/10/F6_Reshma_21-10-2020_Swati_D5.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &amp;lsquo;North&amp;rsquo; is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Pythagoras theorem&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;(Hypotenuse)&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;= (Perpendicular)&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ (Base)&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As per the given information;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/03/F1_Pooja_Madhuri_23.03.2021_D11.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 440px; height: 342px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Using Pythagoras Theorem, the Distance between initial and final point will be:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;=&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;radic;(5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;) +&amp;nbsp;&amp;radic;(5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;=&amp;nbsp;&amp;radic;(25 - 9) +&amp;nbsp;&amp;radic;(25 - 9)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;=&amp;nbsp;&amp;radic;16 +&amp;nbsp;&amp;radic;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;= 4 + 4 = 8 m&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Hence,&lt;strong&gt; Neha is 8 m from his starting point.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Drawing the figure according to the given information:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/05/Screenshot%202021-05-04%20135728.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 421px; height: 335px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thus,&amp;nbsp;the boy is facing&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;south&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;direction at the end.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;South&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/05/Picture1%20%281%29.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 125px; height: 27px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As the question asked is about the direction the boy faces at the end&amp;nbsp;and there is nothing to do with the given distances.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thus, this question can be easily done by ignoring&amp;nbsp;the distances given and&amp;nbsp;just focusing&amp;nbsp;on the turns the boy&amp;nbsp;took.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
